Method Detail

byteIterator

public ByteIterator byteIterator()
Description copied from interface: ByteStrategyType
Compute a fresh ByteIterator, which can be used to provide test data of type byte. The ByteIterator returned should be freshly created. Usually it should not be at its end. However, in rare cases it might make sense to have an empty iterator be computed (e.g., by filtering).
